category: BODY SHOTS
category comment: 

clue: Go against your best interest & you shoot yourself here

response: in the foot

clue: A quick & reckless reaction has you shooting from this body part

response: the hip

clue: Something that has a good effect on you (like a vaccine) is a shot in this

response: the arm

clue: When you brag or boast, you shoot off this body part

response: the mouth

clue: 1775 Bunker Hill order on when you were allowed to shoot

response: when you saw the whites of their eyes

